  ],
  "remarks": "Aghajari Oil & Gas Production Company (AOGPC), also known as Aghajari Oil and Gas Exploitation Company, is an Iranian entity working in the field of energy and a subsidiary of the National Iranian South Oil Company (NISOC). NISOC is a subsidiary of the National Iranian Oil Company (NIOC), which provides support to and is owned by the Government of Iran. Therefore, AOGPC is controlled by an entity, which provides support to the Government of Iran.",
